items.name: Barrel of Sludge

items.description: Some people think this item can be a bit boaring.

items.name: Bottle of Whiskey

items.description: Everyone knows someone who reminds them of what this cactus does, a bit of a prick.

items.name: Camera
items.description: Can be used to stream both on Twitch AND onlyfans!
items.longDescription: This item helps you with the amount of viewers watching your streams.

items.name: Candy
items.description: It is not saltwater taffy. Unless...

items.description: I get that it is candy, but how is it a cane? It is way too small to use to walk.
items.longDescription: Using this item gives nothing of value.

items.name: Cell Phone

items.name: Chill Pill
items.description: Chill Phil, take a big ol chill pill.
items.longDescription: Using this item does nothing of value.

items.description: Everyone loves chocolate cake. EVERYONE. No exceptions. Don't argue with me.
items.longDescription: You can use this item to obtain a pepe skin over with our friends at bake.gg!

items.name: Christmas Tree

items.description: Sometimes you need an item to turn into coins. This is that item, duh.
items.longDescription: Using this item will turn it into 10 million coins. You can use multiple at once with the quantity argument.

items.name: Common Fish
items.description: This fish is pretty common, unlike my ability to come up with good flavor text.

items.name: Cookie
items.description: They said don't eat the dough raw, but that will NOT stop me.
items.longDescription: Using this will do nothing of value.

items.name: Corncob
items.description: Corny jokes are the life blood of this bot.

items.description: Wear these as a SPUR of the moment fashion choice you coward!

items.description: Doug Dimmadome would be proud of this.
items.longDescription: Using this gives you cowboy themed embed colors. (Brown, leather colored)

items.name: Credit Card
items.description: My mom will never know this is missing.

items.description: This is a beef taco, but we all know fish tacos are better.

items.longDescription: Using this item gives you a 10 minutes double xp boost.

items.description: Every time I open these the contents are wet. I hate Dank rewards.

items.longDescription: Using this item gives you black embed colors.

items.longDescription: You can use this item to get a unique pet

items.description: Ducks lay eggs very similarly edible to chicken eggs. One of my favorite differences are that they can be blue depending on the breed of duck.

items.description: It is not suspicious to buy this from the store UNLESS you buy it in bulk and wear a dark hoodie.
items.longDescription: This item can be used to craft things with the craft command.

items.longDescription: Found from the ghost job.

items.description: This is like a fart bottle but like, without the downsides. Crazy item design right?

items.name: Enchanted Badosz's Card
items.description: It's a Badosz card, but enchanted. If only the enchantment DID something!

items.description: Guess the brand that inspired this art. Nope, wrong. It was bud lite.

items.name: Engagement Ring
items.description: Marriage in a MEME game? Disgusting.

items.description: If this was Minecraft, this fish would be used to feed a pet axolotl

items.description: Once a stimulation tool, now a bad meme.

items.description: A pack to get you on your feet in the bot as a new player.

items.name: Odd Eye
items.description: The only one who could see the dark globule in the distance, and now watches over the rest.

items.description: Wait, what does Russian Roulette have to do with cowboys?
items.longDescription: Using this item starts a game of Russian Roulette in chat. 6 people are chosen from all the people who entered, there are 5 bullets in the chamber so only one will walk away with some cash.

items.description: The only thing that rhymes with orange is gullible

items.description: These make a satisfying sound when they fall of the tree in 2005 and make everyone in the house wake up and think a gun went off. Trust me.

items.description: I bet the cactus is thriving in there.

items.description: The lock picking lawyer would make quick work of this I'm ngl to you.

items.name: Patreon Box

items.name: Patreon Pack
items.description: Thanks for supporting us! Now shut up and take my items.

items.description: Pepe certainly did NOT hold me at gunpoint to make a pepe themed box. Who got that idea?

items.description: Can you even believe that this used to be the most expensive item? Now it's a gift you'd give your cousin as a hand me down.

items.description: Some say pepe personally gifted this crown to those who own it. That would be absurd though.

items.name: Pet Collar

items.description: I got the horses in the back, horse tack is attached...

items.name: Pink Plastic Bits

items.description: You wanted pineapple chunks on this, we get it. Too bad.

items.name: Plastic Box
items.description: Imagine if this box existed when plastics were still...

items.longDescription: Found from the police officer job.

items.name: Potato
items.description: Straight from the motherland, home grown and well distributed.

items.description: Did you know purple is my favorite color?

items.description: Some say this is the most rare fish in the sea! Until of course they catch an exotic or legendary fish.

items.name: Rare Pepe
items.description: Ironically enough, the rare pepe is not that rare.

items.name: Sanic Hot Dog

items.name: School Urinal
items.description: Yes, that IS pee around the rim. How did you know?

items.name: Snowflake
items.description: Everyone is a unique snowflake, but not twins right?

items.name: Sound Card
items.description: Sound cards are kinda overrated irl.
items.longDescription: This item helps your odds of getting other streaming items.

items.name: Space Adventure Box
items.description: Do not move, I think I hear a black hole in that box.

items.name: Spider
items.description: Did you know that many people are scared of spiders? AAAAAAAHHHHH GET IT OFF MY SCREE-

items.name: Spooky Mask
items.description: This mask is going to make someone scream, scream of fear or joy? Both!
items.longDescription: Use this mask to scare all your pets into submission. For two weeks they will not run away, but they also will not gain xp, reproduce, or be able to fight.

items.name: Squishy Paw
items.description: A squishy paw that can relieve stress and make you smile. SQUISH! SQUISH! SQUISH! (Yeng Gang rise up). This item was made for a previous team member, Yeng.

items.name: Stack of Cash
items.description: Wait so you gave me a stack of cash and I have to trade it for only 2 things? This sounds more like a coupon.
items.longDescription: Use this item to turn it into banknotes or pizzas. Found from the politician job.

items.name: Star Fragment
items.description: Someone wished a little too hard and BROKE it!

items.name: Stickbug
items.description: It is truly sad to think about how many stickbugs were so well hidden that they became campfire tinder.

items.name: Stonk Coin
items.description: Rotsevni wanted a stonk coin, so Rotsevni got a stonk coin. Winning our competitions pays off!
items.longDescription: Using this item gives you +500% coin multiplier for 24 hours.

items.name: Stonk Machine
items.description: This is a made up machine. It does not exist in real life. Do not search for this irl.
items.longDescription: Use this machine to try and earn some coins from stonk investment. Warning, there is a 10% chance to lose 10% of your wallet from a bad investment! Found from the day trader job.

items.name: Streak Freeze
items.description: Is it just me or is my streak freezing me out of the relationship?
items.longDescription: Using this item will turn it into an active item that lasts 30 days. After it's equipped, you will retain your streak if you run the daily command after missing 1+ days. This is automatically destroyed at that point or when it expires. Better safe than sorry to use this once a month if you have a high streak!

items.name: Sugar Skull
items.description: Celebrate Da de los Muertos by using this, yum!
items.longDescription: Using this item changes your embed colors to be Da de los Muertos themed.

items.name: The Letter
items.description: What's in the letter? Open it up to find out!
items.longDescription: Using this item gives you some messages from the people who won the item competition.

items.name: The Megaphone
items.description: The voice of the people echo through this. This item was made for a previous team member, Alexa.

items.name: Tidepod
items.description: Do not eat this. Do not ignore this warning because memes. Stop eating them. God damn it, stop it.

items.name: Tip Jar
items.description: Why do they slide the tip jar at me "accidentally" every time as if I wasn't going to tip.
items.longDescription: Use this item to get some random rewards every hour. Found from the twitch streamer job.

items.name: Toilet Paper
items.description: If 2-ply is so good for my undercarriage, why not just double wrap it to make 4-ply?

items.name: Townie's Eyes
items.description: Townie sees all.

items.name: Trash
items.description: I think Im done buying trash bags... I always end up throwing them away anyways.

items.name: Treasure Map
items.description: Follow carefully: To the left, take it back now ya'll, one hop this time!
items.longDescription: Using this item spawns a mini game. If you win, you get some coins!

items.name: Tumbleweed
items.description: These are a menace to society, look it up!
items.longDescription: Using this consumes it and does nothing at all.

items.name: Used Diaper
items.description: This is used, but seems like too much for a child. Who wore this?
items.longDescription: Throw this used diaper at someone to prevent them from joining or starting a heist for 12 hours. Found from the house wife job.

items.name: Vaccine
items.description: Momma told me if I get this here shot I can get that there sucker.
items.longDescription: Found from the doctor job.

items.name: Voodoo Doll
items.description: I keep feeling a stabbing feeling in heart. Is it a heart attack or a voodoo doll? Probably just the doll.
items.longDescription: Using this on someone will give them bad luck in grind commands for 6 hours. Bad luck is like the opposite of the horseshoe but more potent.

items.name: Wedding Gift
items.description: Now you have to write thank you notes for all these gifts. Have fun!

items.name: Winning Lottery Ticket
items.description: Is it even that lucky, you probably paid 5b to win.
items.longDescription: Owning this gives you a 2% higher chance at random events spawning.

items.name: Work Box
items.description: Wanna stay home from work and open lootboxes? WOAH TWO IN ONE?

items.name: Worm
items.description: Did you know that the Alaskan Bull Worm from SpongeBob Season 2 Episode 20 is in fact not based in reality?

items.name: Zig's Capybara
items.description: Top 10 best dressed capybaras
